# Question Board — REST Client requests
# Requires the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@username = alice

### Get all questions
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions
x-username: {{username}}

### Post a new question
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
x-username: {{username}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "What is the difference between let and const?"
}

### Upvote a question (replace the id below with a real one from GET /questions)
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions/your-question-id-here/vote
x-username: {{username}}
